Introduction

HyunA&DAWN (Korean: 현아&던; Japanese: ヒョンア＆ダン) was a South Korean duo consisting of HyunA and DAWN. The duo debuted on September 9, 2021 with the mini album 1+1=1.

As of 2022, HyunA and DAWN's contracts expired P Nation.

It is safe to assume the duo has unofficially disbanded due to the couple breaking up in November 2022.
